gft.api
Interface QuoteUpdateListener

All Known Implementing Classes:
QuoteUpdateAdapter
public interface QuoteUpdateListener

The listener interface for receiving quote update events. The class that is interested in processing a quote update event implements this interface (and all the methods it contains). The listener object created from that class is then registered with a Session using its addQuoteUpdateListener method.

Methods of this interface must return quickly, othrwise they will block the stream of asynchronious events.

Author:
Boris Malkin
See Also:
Session.addQuoteUpdateListener(QuoteUpdateListener listener), Session.removeQuoteUpdateListener(QuoteUpdateListener listener)
